  "text": "where Φ is the gravitational potential generated by the subhalo. By substituting (1) into (2), we may derive the equations of motion for f 1 . We choose to do so perturbatively, expanding to leading order in Newton's constant G. In this approximation, the term ∇ x Φ · ∇ v f 1 , which would be of order G 2 , can be dropped [CITATION_1] :",
